Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:56.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あからさまに流していやがる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.00,0:01:58.49,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He's making it obvious that he's just cruising. He's not pushing it to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:58.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,限界近くまで攻めていない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:03.09,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Even so, he's still fast, and\Nmaintaining a high-speed pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:01.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも速い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スピードに乗っている
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:06.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,うまいな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.45,0:02:06.60,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Nice execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:10.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これ程の芸当ができる男だったか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.60,0:02:10.45,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I didn't expect him to be able \Nto pull off such an elegant move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.45,0:02:13.96,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I didn't realize he was so \Nskillful until I drove behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:12.22,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こうして後ろに追て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:14.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,始めて分かる事だな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:15.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それにしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:19.48,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That aside, his car seems so fun to drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:19.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとまあ気持ちよさそに走る車だ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:22.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ショッキングなくらいだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:25.54,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's quite shocking to see a driver who can compete at this high of a level.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.52,0:02:25.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな領域でバトルする奴がいたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.99,0:02:30.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のNSXも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:33.99,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Has my NSX ever looked \Nlike that from the outside ?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.95,0:02:34.22,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,外から見ていてあんな風に見えた時があっただろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.46,0:02:39.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,引き込まれる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.69,0:02:39.60,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm being sucked in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:43.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この心地良いリズムに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:46.80,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm being sucked in\N by this pleasant rhythm...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:45.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,引き込まれてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,シンクロしていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:49.12,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...and getting synchronized.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負事に絶対はないっちゅう事や
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.55,0:03:00.76,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,You can never be certain about\Nthe outcome of a competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:07.67,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{tashika}We were outsmarted in data collection, but it's still within our expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.78,0:03:03.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確かにデータの収集では一杯食わされたが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:06.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ギリギリ想定の範囲内とは言える
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,万が一を考えて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.67,0:03:13.72,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{manga}We ran our simulation with a reasonable margin, just in case. We're not stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:11.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,データにはゲタをはかせてシミュレーションをしているんや
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.31,0:03:13.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,わしらもバカやない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,１５秒とはいかんまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:20.63,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{juugo}Maybe not by 15 seconds, but our \Ncar still has an absolute advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:20.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車には絶対アドバンテージは残ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.44,0:03:24.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やはりサーキットではありえへん事は峠では起こる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.50,0:03:25.71,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{yahari}After all, unlike circuits, unexpected things happen on mountain passes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでは相手のドライバーが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.71,0:03:30.21,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{kokomade}So far, our opponent is doing an excellent job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:30.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ものすごいええ仕事をしとるっちゅう事や
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:32.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ負けん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:33.15,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{mada}We haven't lost yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:35.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,次は家の大将がやり返す番や
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.00,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,, This time, our leader will \Nturn the situation around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:40.55,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{kono}If he can manage this second run,\Nthere's no reason for us to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:39.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この二本目さえしのげば負ける材料はない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:42.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,圧倒的優位は動かんで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.25,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{attouteki}Nothing can shake our absolute advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:52.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この心地良さも　何処かで終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:52.00,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This pleasant feeling will \Neventually come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:58.10,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}There'll be a moment when\Nit will switch to combat mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.15,0:03:56.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,戦闘モードに切り替わる瞬間がいずれ来る
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が一本目にした事と同じように
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:02.83,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He'll make a full-throttle dash\Nlike I did in the first run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,容赦ない全開スパートをかけてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:07.43,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それに俺とNSXも持ちこたえられなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:10.04,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}If my NSX and I can't keep up \Nwith it, this battle will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:10.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その瞬間にこのバトルは終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:14.22,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:16.00,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Where...? Where are you\Ngoing to make your move ?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:16.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこで来る
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:28.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これは
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:30.82,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is beyond our expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:30.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やはり想定外だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:34.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,流していてFDがこんなに速いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:36.61,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}An FD's cruising speed can't be that fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:36.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ありえね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,行ける
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.12,def2,.KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can do it. I'm focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,集中している
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:45.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:47.85,def2,.KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is fun. \NI've wanted to fight a battle like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.92,0:04:47.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなバトルがしたかったんだ
