Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:11.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今の俺は気持ちの準備が出来ていない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:12.00,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm not mentally ready yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.40,0:05:16.30,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Why did my spurt fail in the first run ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.46,0:05:15.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一本目のスパートが失敗したのはなぜだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:19.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺と久保さんが考えていたよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:22.72,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Is he better than Kubo and I had imagined ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,目の前にいるこの男は上を行くのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.72,0:05:24.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.91,0:05:25.00,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車のアドバンテージは本当にあるのかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:29.15,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Does my car really \Nhave an advantage ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:29.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それとも
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:31.49,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Or am I the problem ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺自身の問題なのか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:33.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:37.26,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{mattaku}I have so many doubts that\NI have nothing I can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:34.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,疑心暗鬼だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拠り所を無くしている
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,立て直すきっかけがない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.14,0:05:40.64,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{tatenaosu}I don't know how to turn this around.{have no clue of how to turn this around.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:51.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうすればいい　兄貴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.79,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What should I do, Brother ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:00.85,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日もベストタイムを更新してたな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:02.15,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,You beat your best time again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.99,0:06:03.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,タイムのばらつきもなく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:05.90,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,You're noticeably getting better\N because your times are consistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.12,0:06:05.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,確実によくなってきてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.24,0:06:09.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴のアドバイスがいつも的確なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.75,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,Your advice is always spot on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何をどうすればいいタイムが出るのが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:13.75,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,You know exactly what to \Ndo to improve the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.22,0:06:13.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ホントによく知ってるよな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:19.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サーキットは　やっぱ面白いや
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.20,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,Circuit racing is really fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:24.30,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,I like the fact that my time \Nclearly shows how I've improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:22.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,自分が速くなるのが
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,数字ではっきり分かるのがいいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:28.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これだけ思いきりアクセルを踏めるシチュエーションは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.30,0:06:30.20,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,You can't find a situation where\N you can go flat out elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.33,0:06:29.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,他にないからな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.00,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:32.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:34.35,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,But you have the right aptitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.00,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は筋がいい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:37.00,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,Your rate of improvement is incredibly fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.48,0:06:37.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,上達するスピードが考えられないくらい速い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.19,0:06:41.85,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　才能あると思うぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:43.10,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,I think you have talent, Gou.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.64,0:07:11.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:12.00,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What was it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スタート前のあの時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:17.33,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What did my brother say right \Nbefore the start of the race ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:17.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,兄貴は何を言ってたんだっけ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はラッキーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.65,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,You're fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:24.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車と峠を愛する物として
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:26.50,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,As a man who loves cars and mountain passes, you can't be happier than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:26.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これ程の幸せはないだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:29.59,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前にできる最高の走りをしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.35,0:07:33.50,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,Do your very best. \NUse everything you've learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:33.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで培ってきた物を全て出しきって見ろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.36,0:07:36.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そして　楽しめ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.65,0:07:36.55,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFE8F&}And enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ねね　真子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:49.83,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Hey, Mako...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:54.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真司君って　ちょっと拓海くんに似てると思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:54.83,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,...doesn't Shinji remind you of Takumi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,思う　思う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.83,0:07:55.90,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,He does, he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:58.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,会った時からなんとなくだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.90,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,The moment I saw you, I felt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.40,0:08:04.33,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,You just seem to have a similar\Natmosphere, especially the pure side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:01.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,きっと雰囲気が似てるんだよね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,特にピュアな所が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:05.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拓海くんって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.19,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,Who's Takumi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:09.71,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,プロジェクトDの藤原拓海だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.70,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Project D's Fujiwara Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:12.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで見てれば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:15.30,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,You'll be able to see\N his driving from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:15.26,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拓海くんの走ってるとこを見られるはずだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.45,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,プロジェクトDの藤原拓海と
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.41,0:08:23.32,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,Do you know Project D's Fujiwara Takumi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:22.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,知り合いなんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:23.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まーね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.32,0:08:24.75,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.59,0:08:26.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,前にバトルして負けてるけどね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.75,0:08:27.28,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,We fought a battle against him, and lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:27.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,バトル
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.28,0:08:28.48,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,A battle ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:36.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってきたぜ　なんとなく
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.80,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm beginning to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.36,0:08:41.01,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この男が俺の上を行くというのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:43.34,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}If he's better than me, it's pointless\Nto try and figure out what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.53,0:08:43.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ジタバタしても始まらない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.18,0:08:47.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スピードとテクニックを追求する者として
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:48.25,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}As a driver who pursues\N speed and technique...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,未知の何かに出会えるならば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:53.15,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}...if I can see something unprecedented, it should be a thrilling opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:53.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,痺れるほどラッキーなチャンスかもな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.98,0:08:57.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつでも来い
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.15,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Make your move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,けど　俺もしつこいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.15,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}But remember, I'm persistent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:04.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そこ頃　アタシたちはコンビでさ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:07.95,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,We were partners back then, and we were\N confident that we would never lose in our area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.97,0:09:07.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,地元では負けない自信があったんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:11.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真子さんたちが　藤原拓海とバトルを
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.95,0:09:11.80,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}They fought a battle against Fujiwara Takumi ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.00,0:09:16.90,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,Takumi had something\Nsuperior, even back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:13.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あの頃から拓海くんは
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:16.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ずば抜けたなにかがあったよね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:21.60,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,Even if you lose, you feel refreshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:19.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,負けても悔しいと思うより
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,爽やかな気持ちになっちゃうような
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.62,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いいオーラなんだと思う
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:28.80,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,He has a pleasant aura. He's got a soothing smile once he gets out of his car, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車降りれば癒し系な顔だし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうなんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:35.28,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,Is that so ? Is it cool to\Nbe able to drive a car well ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車の運転がうまいって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:34.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,格好いい事なんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:37.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それは間違いないと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:37.90,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,That's a definite yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:40.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,男はルックスじゃないと　アタシは思うね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.90,0:09:41.00,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,When it comes to a guy \NI don't think his looks matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:45.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どんなジャンルでも一流の仕事ができる男は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.09,0:09:45.90,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Any guy who's the best in his field...{no matter what he looks like}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:49.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,顔とか関係なく必ずもてるもんね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:50.28,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,...is always popular no \Nmatter what he looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.93,0:09:53.29,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真子さんもそう思いますか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.00,0:09:53.50,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,Do you think so too, Mako ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:53.90,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:56.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,チー　またかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:59.00,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Not again. She's pretty\Ncunning behind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当は腹黒い女なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:03.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真子なんて　特に速い男にはイチコロよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.54,0:10:03.55,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Mako is head over heels for fast drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:07.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そう言うのに昔　片思いしてた事もあるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.55,0:10:07.46,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,She had a secret crush \Non a guy like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:09.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,調子に乗ってるでしょう　沙雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.46,0:10:11.88,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,Hey, don't get carried\Naway too much, or I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それ以上言うと殺すわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だってホントの事じゃー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.90,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,But it was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そ　そうなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:15.00,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\pos(424,437.333)}She did ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:15.00,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Hey, you're blushing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.91,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まっ　冗談はともかく
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:22.88,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,Her joke aside, have you ever seen a race in the circuit before, Shinji ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:21.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真司くん　サーキットでレース見た事ある
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:26.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大勢の観客が見ている中で走るドライバーたちは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:29.90,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,A handful of chosen drivers, who race\Nin front of crowds, are admired heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:29.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,選ばれたひとにぎりの憧れのヒーローなんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,憧れの　ヒーロー
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.45,0:10:33.00,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Admired heroes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.62,0:10:36.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも今日このステージを走る四人のドライバーは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:41.03,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,The four drivers who are competing in this stage today are truly special to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:38.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アタシたちから見たら
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:41.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に特別な存在なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:49.24,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,{circuit}They're even more awesome than the \Nprofessional drivers who race in the circuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:44.55,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,サーキットを走るプロのドライバーよりも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:49.21,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,寧ろ　遥かに格好いいって感じてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:03.76,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,走りを楽しむという概念は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.35,0:11:07.00,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,The idea of enjoying driving\Nvaries according to the driver's skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:07.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ドライバーのスキルによってそれぞれ違う
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.15,0:11:10.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ゼロ理論では
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:14.05,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,In my Zero theory, enjoyment is \Nonly attained by high level drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:13.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しむという感覚はレベルの高い状態なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ギャンブル的な走りで
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:23.07,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,Those who regard adrenaline-pumping risky \Nsituations as enjoyment are still low-level drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:20.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ただアドレナリンが出ている状況を楽しいと思ってるうちは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まだレベルが低い
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:25.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,多くのことをコントロールするスキルがあってこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:30.41,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,{ooku}You can relax your mind under pressure and tension\Nonly when you have the skills to control various factors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:29.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,プレッシャーや緊張感に飲み込まれない余裕が持てる
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その余裕こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:35.38,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,{sono}Don't you think that such a relaxed \Nmental state is synonymous with enjoyment ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.28,0:11:34.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しむことと同義語だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:36.25,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に言えば
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:44.00,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,{gyaku}Conversely, if your mind is not relaxed, your brain can't function at its best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:39.86,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,心に余裕を残せている状態でなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:43.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,人の脳というのはベストなポテンシャルを発揮できない
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:52.70,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,{top}I think, to a lesser extent, it's similar to a top\Nathlete's ability to reach a special mental state.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:48.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,トップアスリートが持っているゾーンに入る感覚も
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう物の延長線上にあると
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:52.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は考えている
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.64,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:55.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんていうかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:57.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,池田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.64,0:12:01.41,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,Ikeda, you're a nice guy, but your problem is your over-philosophical character.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:12:01.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はいい男だが　いつも理屈っぽ過ぎるのが難点だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:05.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,坊主なだけに何か線香臭いんだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.41,0:12:06.19,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,I can almost smell the incense,\Nprobably because you're a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,悪かったな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.30,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me for\Nsmelling like incense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,線香臭くて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.43,0:12:13.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ゼロ理論は確かよく出来ていると思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:15.00,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,Your Zero theory is very well-constructed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.00,0:12:20.17,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,...but what I wanted to tell\NGou was a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.06,0:12:17.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど俺が豪に伝えたかったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それとは　ちょっと違う
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:35.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今三番ヘアピンを通過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:37.43,def2,...MAN....,0,0,0,,They just passed hairpin 3.\NThe gap is negligible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:37.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,差はほとんどありません
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:40.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の真意は
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.00,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,I wanted to remind him of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:49.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どこでスパートをかけてくるつもりなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:51.93,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I have a hunch of where\Nyou're going to make your spurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.01,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今ならなんとなく分かるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.60,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コースに関する情報量が地元なだけに多すぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:59.12,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}As a local driver, I know too much about this course, which makes me blind to simple things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.06,0:12:59.26,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,かえって単純な事が見え難くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,単純な事なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:07.38,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:11.78,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,目の前にいる相手に絶対負けないという気持ちだ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.62,0:13:12.95,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,...eagerness to defeat the\Nopponent right before his eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,速いのは俺だという
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:16.35,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,{hayai}...and also a strong fighting spirit \Nbacked by the confidence of not losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,強烈な闘争心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:19.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキっぽくて結構
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.58,0:13:23.79,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,Call me childish, but that's the \Nbasics of street racing, isn't it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,走り屋の原点というのは　そういう物だろ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.82,0:13:27.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前はアドレナリンを良くないものと決めているけど
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:30.68,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,You think adrenaline is bad, but I disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.21,0:13:29.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,おれはそうは思わない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.79,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,初心者のギャンブル走りとは基本的に違う
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:34.00,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,It's fundamentally different from\Nrisky maneuvers by amateurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:40.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,高いスキルを持っている二人だからこそ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.00,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,Because they possess such high skills...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:49.00,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,...they were done with course strategy and vehicle tuning even before the race began.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,車の調整とかコースの攻略とか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:46.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,頭で考えるべきことは
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.49,0:13:48.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,全て走り出す前に終わっているからな
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:51.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,スタートしてしまえば
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:54.00,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,After it begins, they just\Nhave to be eager to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.69,0:13:53.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう遮二無二攻めるだけでいい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:56.14,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今日に限っては
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:14:00.59,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,Today, the higher the \Nblood-adrenaline level the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:59.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アドレナリンの血中濃度は高ければ高いほどいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:03.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,血中濃度とは　言い方が医者っぽい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.59,0:14:04.15,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,"Blood-adrenaline level." \NYou sound like a physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.10,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,I can almost smell the antiseptic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前こそ　消毒液臭いぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　あまりにもリスキーで
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:12.57,def2,..IKEDA...,0,0,0,,Still, it's too risky.\NI don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は好きじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.43,0:14:13.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,しかたあるまい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.57,0:14:13.70,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:16.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それが峠だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.05,0:14:20.73,def2,...RIN....,0,0,0,,That's what a mountain pass is all about, and that's how you enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,峠が楽しいというのは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:20.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう事だ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:29.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,来た
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.15,0:14:30.15,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,There !
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.54,0:14:51.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すごい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.65,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.10,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What happened ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,豪さんが違う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:57.20,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Gou looked different.\NHe was never like that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:57.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今までと違う
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:15:03.17,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}His red car looked excited.\NThat's never happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:00.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,赤い車が弾んで見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,今までこんな事無かった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:06.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,泣いてるの　真子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.96,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Are you crying, Mako ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:10.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだろう　歓喜わまっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:11.00,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,I don't know why,\Nbut I'm so moved.{moved}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:15.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ビリビリと空気を震わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:17.60,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,It felt like something traveled through the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.91,0:15:17.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なにか伝わてきたの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:20.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どっちのドライバーもすごいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:20.74,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,Both drivers are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:24.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何だ　この感じ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.28,0:15:24.28,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What's this feeling ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.28,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Am I envious ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:28.26,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,羨ましい　のかな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:31.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真子さんを泣かすほど感激させるなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:34.26,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Can I impress Mako so much\Nthat she has to shed tears ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.11,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕に出来るだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.37,0:15:38.26,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,走りたい　僕もあんな風に
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:38.45,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I want to drive like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.25,0:15:50.06,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.41,0:15:53.80,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This must be it. It's the point where I made my move in the first run.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.56,0:15:52.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一本目俺が勝負を仕掛けたら
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:54.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じこのポイントだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:56.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,分かりやすくフェアな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.85,0:15:58.14,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's the simplest and easiest answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:15:58.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,最もシンプルな答えだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.09,0:16:01.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,温存していたものは全て吐き出す
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:01.87,def2,.KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I'm going to use all the \Nstrength I've been saving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負だ　北条豪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.54,def2,.KEISUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Let's begin our battle, Hojo Gou !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.05,0:16:12.47,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだろうと思ったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.14,0:16:12.45,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:17.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,人事を尽くして天命を待つ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:20.63,def2,.RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I feel very much like,\N"Do your best and leave the rest."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.34,0:16:19.66,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな心境だぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:26.90,def2,.RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I've done everything I could, \Nso drive as you see fit.{like.}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.51,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,出来ることは全てやってきた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.46,0:16:26.33,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,後は　お前の思うがままに走れ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:30.65,def2,.RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You outgrew me a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.96,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は　もうとっくに俺の手を離れている
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:34.20,def2,.RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}From here, your strength\Nwill be put to the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:34.15,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここから試されるのは　お前の人間力だ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,攻めろ　啓介
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.20,0:16:36.80,def2,.RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Go for it, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すげー
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.41,0:17:10.84,def2,...MAN....,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.80,def2,...MAN....,0,0,0,,{It's a that sound that cuts through the air.}Is that the sound of the car \Nslicing through the air ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.99,0:17:13.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,大気を切り裂く音っていうのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:19.38,def2,...MAN....,0,0,0,,{tohge}I've never heard it on a mountain pass before, but the sheer speed gave me chills. {It's scary.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:16.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,峠で聞いたこと無かったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:18.65,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ぞっとするほどスピードを感じる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:20.77,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,FDやばい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:22.19,def2,...MAN....,0,0,0,,That FD is wicked. It's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヤバすぎだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:31.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,第四セクションの中間計測が来てます
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:32.56,def2,...MAN....,0,0,0,,I've got the intermediate time\Nfrom section 4. Have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:32.85,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,見てください
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.77,0:17:35.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アカン
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:37.50,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,This is bad. It's too fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:37.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,早過ぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:40.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,想定した車の限界をドライバーが超えとる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:41.00,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,They're using their cars'\N potential beyond the preset limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.83,0:17:42.54,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,エスケープゾーンのないとこで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:44.80,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{escape}We shouldn't maintain this pace in a course without any escape zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:44.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなペースに付き合っとったらアカン
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.79,0:17:49.64,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,北条はん　アンタ命が幾つあっても足りまへんで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:49.50,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Hojo, you only have one life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:56.79,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}When it comes to a street fight, Project D is a notch above us because they have more experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.24,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,公道の喧嘩なら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.48,0:17:55.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,プロジェクトDのほうが喧嘩慣れしとる分　一枚上ですわ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:59.01,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この領域に踏み込まずに戦う事が
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.79,0:18:01.07,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{kono}Our strategy was to race\Nwithout reaching that level.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.28,0:18:01.00,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,我々の戦略やったはず
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:05.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,喧嘩ではなくモータースポーツとして戦えば
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:07.50,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{kenka}If we could fight this battle as a \Nmotor sport, we would be superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.64,0:18:06.67,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらが上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.26,0:18:08.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ムキになるな　大将
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.30,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Don't get overeager.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:10.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,敵も苦しいんやで
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.00,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Our opponent is struggling just as much.{equally struggling.}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.54,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He can't maintain such a pace for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.57,0:18:14.42,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなペース　長くはもたぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:18.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しいぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.61,0:18:18.55,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.85,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's not about logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.69,0:18:20.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,理屈じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.65,0:18:23.30,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,目の前は走る奴がいて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:27.30,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You can't just allow your\Nopponent to pull away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.79,0:18:25.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それが少しずつ離れていくのを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.82,0:18:27.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,黙って見送れる訳がない
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,逃げる車がいれば追う
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:31.65,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}If I see a car trying to \Noutrun me, I must chase it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,本能なんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.30,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}That's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:35.90,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}It makes my blood boil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.42,0:18:35.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,体の芯が沸騰してるぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:45.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すげーなあいつら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:48.65,def2,.MINAGAWA.,0,0,0,,They're incredible. \NThey give me the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:48.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が見てもぞっとする
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:50.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ガチでどつき合いだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.00,def2,KOBAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,It's like a fist-fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.21,0:18:53.84,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アクセル全開でインカットする時のラインが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:57.90,def2,KOBAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,Their exit lines at full throttle are closer to the outer edge by a few centimeters compared to their previous run.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.17,0:18:57.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,先の一本目よりもさらに数センチ奥にずれてる
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんな攻め方をしていたら
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:02.35,def2,.MINAGAWA.,0,0,0,,If they continue fighting like that, \Nthey could lose control at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつ破綻してもおかしくないな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.62,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,集中力も長くは続かないだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:05.85,def2,.MINAGAWA.,0,0,0,,Their concentration won't last forever.{so long.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.74,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,破滅的な決着でないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:08.98,def2,.MINAGAWA.,0,0,0,,I hope this won't end in tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:09.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,祈るしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:11.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど何ていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:14.62,def2,.MINAGAWA.,0,0,0,,But for some reason, I'm a little envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:13.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,少し羨ましいような気分だな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.62,0:19:19.45,def2,KOBAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,Same here.\NI'm deeply impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.64,0:19:15.94,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同感ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:18.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ハートにドスンとくるものがある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:21.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,格好いいじゃないですか　あいつら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:22.45,def2,KOBAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,They look awesome, don't they ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.18,0:19:25.20,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのDNAは俺の中にも間違いないなくある
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:25.90,def2,KOBAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,There's no doubt I share\Nthe same DNA as theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,純粋にスプリントでは負けたくないっていう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:30.65,def2,.MINAGAWA.,0,0,0,,It's the stubbornness and pride of \Nsimply hating to lose in a sprint race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.00,0:19:30.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,意地とプライド
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:34.40,def2,.MINAGAWA.,0,0,0,, Without it, we wouldn't be\Nracing in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.75,0:19:34.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも　それがなければレースなんてやっていない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:36.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,無性に走りたくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.21,0:19:37.60,def2,KOBAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,I want to race so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.01,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あのテンションのなかに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.60,0:19:40.45,def2,KOBAYAKAWA,0,0,0,,I want to jump into \Nthat high-tension race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:40.70,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,飛び込んでみたくなりますね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:03.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いつもと景色が違う
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.99,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}The view is different from usual.\NI'm going at an extraordinary pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.04,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,未体験ゾーンか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:06.89,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.02,0:20:09.43,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}{yamerarenai}I can't stop. How can\NI quit having this much fun ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:09.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな楽しい事を止められんかよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.76,0:20:26.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,速い
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:26.60,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He's fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:33.10,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,アンダーも出れば
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:35.65,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Not only is my car under-steering, \Nbut it's over-steering as well ?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,オーバーにも成る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.53,0:20:39.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒルクライムでフロントタイヤがここまで来ることは無かったぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.12,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I've never worn the front tires \Nso much in a hill-climb before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:42.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,同じはずだ　奴も
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:42.41,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}He must have the same problem.{be in the same position.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:43.99,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:44.38,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Dammit !
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.12,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ウオームアップスタートか
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:55.90,def2,MATSUMOTO.,0,0,0,,Warming up already ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.37,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まだヒルクライム　ケリはついてないぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:59.29,def2,MATSUMOTO.,0,0,0,,The hill-climb hasn't ended yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.09,0:21:01.02,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,二本目で決着がつかなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:02.65,def2,MATSUMOTO.,0,0,0,,If they can't settle the match in this second run, there will be a third.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,三本目に行くんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.02,def2,MATSUMOTO.,0,0,0,,Don't be in such a hurry, just relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:05.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あまり気負わず　落ち着いていこうぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.27,0:21:08.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ　でも　三本目はない気がします
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:08.90,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Right, but I don't think \Nthere will be a third run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.88,0:21:10.44,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この二本目で終わりますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:11.05,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,It will be over in this second run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.88,0:21:13.72,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,藤原が予言すると　説得力があるな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:15.03,def2,.RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,Fujiwara, your prediction sounds \Nconvincing, but why do you think so ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:15.03,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何故そう思う
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.62,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,啓介さん　乗れてるからです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:18.65,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,Keisuke's in excellent condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:20.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒にプラクティスもやってきてるから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.65,0:21:23.29,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,I can feel it because\Nwe practice together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:22.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか分かるんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:25.48,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっとすごいなとは思ってたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.29,0:21:29.73,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,{zutto}I always thought he was great, but he's extraordinary this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.83,0:21:28.88,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,啓介さん　今週はちょっと尋常じゃなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:31.32,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちプロじゃないから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:37.45,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,{oretachi}We're not pros, so our driving precision \Nvaries by our physical condition at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:33.09,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,その時の体調によって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.17,0:21:36.90,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,走るたびに微妙なドライビングの精度がばらつくんですけど
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:41.53,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,この大事な時にコンディションのピークが来てしまう事がすごいです
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:41.45,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,{kono}He raised his condition to the highest at this critical moment. That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.89,0:21:44.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがによく見てるな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.00,def2,.RYOSUKE..,0,0,0,,You're observant as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.85,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,相手もすごいドライバーだと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:48.74,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,I think our opponent\Nis an impressive driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:51.56,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　今の啓介さんはその上ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:51.56,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,But Keisuke is better at the current moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:54.69,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,敵じゃなくて本当によかったと思います
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:57.26,def2,..TAKUMI..,0,0,0,,I'm glad he's not my opponent.\NHe gives off a dangerous aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:57.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,あんなヤバイオーラの出てる人は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.29,0:22:07.46,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,三秒以上の全開区間があれば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:10.22,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I can gain on him a bit if I can go\Nflat-out for 3 seconds or longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:09.18,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僅かに詰められる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:16.84,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I have to shed every tenth of a second I can in order to maintain the gap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.95,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,コンマ一秒ずつでもいい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:13.27,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,拾い集めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:16.82,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これ以上差が開くわけにはいかねえって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:19.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,このコーナーの先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:22.70,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}There's a flat-out segment of\N4 seconds after{head of} that curve.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.91,0:22:21.61,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,約四秒の全開区間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:24.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ひろうぜ　確実に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.70,0:22:25.86,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I must take every opportunity one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.51,0:22:25.92,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一つずつの勝負
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:29.57,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,速いか　進入スピード
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:29.72,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Is my entry speed too fast ?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.82,0:22:32.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　行け
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.00,0:22:33.05,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}No, I've gotta go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.94,0:22:34.58,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ケツを出し気味に４ドリで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:35.50,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Swing the tail a bit,\Nand use four-wheel drift...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:38.36,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,踏め　コンマ１秒も無くせない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:38.55,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Step on it. I can't even\Nlose a tenth of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:41.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,攻めなければ　離される
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:41.60,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I have to keep on pushing, or I'll fall behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:43.63,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,攻めなければ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.65,0:22:44.00,def2,...GOU....,0,0,0,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I have to push it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.23,0:23:15.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真子さん　沙雪さん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:18.45,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,Mako, Sayuki, I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:18.16,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕もう行かないと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.35,0:23:20.08,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,行くって何処へ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:20.20,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Go ? Where ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:22.65,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,The best part of the\N show is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.28,0:23:22.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,これからがいっちゃんいいとこだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.53,0:23:24.98,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒にここでダウンヒル見ようよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.65,0:23:25.34,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Why don't we watch the\Ndown-hill race from here together ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.12,0:23:26.34,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,いや　僕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.34,0:23:27.35,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:29.06,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,I must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:29.19,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてもいかなきゃいけなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:32.35,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたのかもん
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:32.77,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,What's wrong with him ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:33.73,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さー
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.77,0:23:33.94,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.57,0:23:49.39,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.70,0:23:49.78,def2,..THREE...,0,0,0,,We won !
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.63,0:23:52.83,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やった　やった　すげーよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.78,0:23:52.70,def2,..KENJI...,0,0,0,,It's awesome, just awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.90,0:23:55.37,def2,.IKETANI..,0,0,0,,Just like Takahashi Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:55.13,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが高橋啓介
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.19,0:23:57.38,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱ者が違いますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:57.70,def2,..ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,He's in a class by himself !
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.70,0:24:01.11,def2,..ITSUKI..,0,0,0,,Now Takumi, you should win, too !
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:01.17,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,よーし　拓海　絶対勝てよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.39,0:24:05.18,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここまでやってくれれば
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.59,0:24:07.80,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,They've done so well that\Nthe outcome is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.37,0:24:07.50,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,もう勝ちも負けもないやろ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.62,0:24:10.41,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ストップウオッチは嘘つかん
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.72,0:24:11.40,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,The stopwatch doesn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.27,0:24:12.93,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の仕上げた車に
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.40,0:24:16.40,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,The car I built must have been possessed by something. It's like a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.16,0:24:15.87,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,何かが乗り移って出た奇跡やろな
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.21,0:24:19.23,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,長いことこの業界におるが
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.40,0:24:22.87,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,I've been in the biz for a long time, \Nbut this is some kind of culture shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.50,0:24:21.80,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょっとしたカルチャーショックやで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.67,0:24:24.05,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,すごいもんや
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.87,0:24:26.70,def2,...KUBO...,0,0,0,,Humans are incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.13,0:24:26.68,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,人間ちゅうのは
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.56,0:24:44.40,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真子さん
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.77,0:24:45.80,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,Mako, please watch me from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.69,0:24:45.97,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで見ててください
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.72,0:24:50.52,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,僕は　藤原拓海を負かすかもしれないです
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.87,0:24:50.30,def2,..SHINJI..,0,0,0,,I might defeat Fujiwara Takumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.73,0:24:59.50,def2,...MAKO...,0,0,0,,What is that supposed to mean ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.85,0:24:59.07,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,どういう事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.21,0:25:00.81,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,真司くんって
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.50,0:25:01.00,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,Could Shinji be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.62,0:25:02.49,日文-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.65,0:25:02.41,def2,..SAYUKI..,0,0,0,,No way !
